{
  "text": "EBOV, when dried in the same media on solid surfaces (plastic and glass) and stored at 4 \u00b0C, showed a decrease in the viral titre of 4 logs over 14 days. When virus-containing tissue culture media was dried onto glass, the virus survived for over 50 days [CITATION_1] .",
